Call me evil if you will, it is of no consequence to me, and if it helps make things easy for you, then so be it. I however prefer to think of it as a difference in motivation, with the ones you call evil not fettered by the conventional restraints of morality and, therefore willing to do more. Yes, I and my kin are such men and women of will, and we are more numerous than you might think. <br>
<br>
